        {
            "id": "http://yoursite.com/2020/06/14/python%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E8%BF%9B%E5%BA%A6%E6%9D%A1/",
            "url": "http://yoursite.com/2020/06/14/python%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E8%BF%9B%E5%BA%A6%E6%9D%A1/",
            "title": "python动态打印进度条",
            "date_published": "2020-06-14T03:42:06.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h2><p>在等待某一个漫长的进程时，不借助进度条我们是不知道执行进度的(占总比例)，尤其是调用有接入限制的API。</p>\n<h2 id=\"简单进度\"><a href=\"#简单进度\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"简单进度\"></a>简单进度</h2><p>缺点是只能看，不能用，<del>可以忽悠客户</del></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> time</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> random</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> range(<span class=\"number\">1</span>,<span class=\"number\">101</span>): <span class=\"comment\">#</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"string\">\"\\r下载进度：%.2f%%\"</span> %(float(i/<span class=\"number\">100</span>*<span class=\"number\">100</span>)),end=<span class=\"string\">' '</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    time.sleep(<span class=\"number\">0.1</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"自定义设置总量\"><a href=\"#自定义设置总量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自定义设置总量\"></a>自定义设置总量</h2><p>也是只能看，而且占用内存较多(计算庞大)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> os,sys</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">ProgressBar</span><span class=\"params\">(num)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"\"\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">    :param num: 传入进度条总量值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">    :return:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">    \"\"\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    total = <span class=\"number\">50</span>  <span class=\"comment\"># 进度条长度共20个“#”</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> num == <span class=\"number\">0</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(<span class=\"string\">'传入参数不可为0，仅接受int类型'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">elif</span> type(num) != int:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(<span class=\"string\">'传入参数仅接受int类型'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> item <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> range(num + <span class=\"number\">1</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">            test_num = int((item / num) * <span class=\"number\">100</span>)  <span class=\"comment\"># 当前百分比</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            step = int(test_num / (<span class=\"number\">100</span> / total))  <span class=\"comment\"># 一个‘#’的在100% 内的占比</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            now = <span class=\"string\">r\"[ %s%s ]%s\"</span> % (<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> * step, <span class=\"string\">' '</span> * (total - step), str(test_num))</span><br><span class=\"line\">            sys.stdout.write(<span class=\"string\">\"\\r%s%%\"</span> % now)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            sys.stdout.flush()</span><br><span class=\"line\">            time.sleep(<span class=\"number\">0.1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">ProgressBar(<span class=\"number\">100</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"tqdm库使用\"><a href=\"#tqdm库使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"tqdm库使用\"></a>tqdm库使用</h2><ol>\n<li><p>导入库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pip install -i https://tuna.pypi.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple tqdm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>方法简介</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>tqdm类：可迭代对象，前缀名，总步长<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">tqdm</span><span class=\"params\">(object)</span>:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">__init__</span><span class=\"params\">(self,iterable=None,desc=None,total=None)</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>可迭代对象<code>tqdm(range(n,m))</code>=<code>trange(n,m)</code></li>\n<li>实例化进度条再使用<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">bar = tqdm(lista)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> bar:</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">pass</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>简单实例<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> time</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> tqdm <span class=\"keyword\">import</span> trange</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">from</span> tqdm <span class=\"keyword\">import</span> tqdm</span><br><span class=\"line\">start = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">end = <span class=\"number\">122</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">li = list(range(start,end))</span><br><span class=\"line\">times = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">start_time = time.time()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> tqdm(li):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    times+=<span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"number\">0</span>==times%<span class=\"number\">2</span>):</span><br><span class=\"line\">        time.sleep(<span class=\"number\">0.1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">end_time = time.time()</span><br><span class=\"line\">cost_time = end_time - start_time</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(cost_time)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>原时间为5s，调用库后6s，因此调用进度条虽然可以看到实时进程，但是迭代也消耗了时空。</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "程序设计"
            ]
        }
    ]
